 Isn't Moore as contemptible as he claims Heston is, for capitalizing on those kids hurt at the school? He's as much an ambulance chaser as any I've heard of -using their pain to push his agenda.<br>
<br>
 He commented in the movie on the american media's fascination with guns crimes.<br>
 I challenge that, and challenge him to also to use his big name and screen time to bring these factors of that biased media to light:<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://enquirer.com/editions/2002/06/03/loc_bronson_armed_pilots.html">enquirer.com/editions/2002/06/03/loc_bronson_armed_pilots.html</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
